    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Here's how do do it directly (without an explicit extra loop) by defining the appropriate <code>Comparator</code>:</p>\n\n<pre><code>int keyOfMaxValue = Collections.max(\n                        yourMap.entrySet(), \n                        new Comparator&lt;Entry&lt;Double,Integer&gt;&gt;(){\n                            @Override\n                            public int compare(Entry&lt;Integer, Integer&gt; o1, Entry&lt;Integer, Integer&gt; o2) {\n                                return o1.getValue() &gt; o2.getValue()? 1:-1;\n                            }\n                        }).getKey();\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
