    "body" : "<p>you can do like that</p>\n\n<pre><code>HashMap&lt;Integer,Integer&gt; hm = new HashMap&lt;Integer,Integer&gt;();\nhm.put(1,10);\nhm.put(2,45);\nhm.put(3,100);\nIterator&lt;Integer&gt; it = hm.keySet().iterator();\nInteger fk = it.next();\nInteger max = hm.get(fk);\nwhile(it.hasNext()) {\n    Integer k = it.next();\n    Integer val = hm.get(k);\n    if (val &gt; max){\n         max = val;\n         fk=k;\n    }\n}\nSystem.out.println(\"Max Value \"+max+\" is associated with \"+fk+\" key\");\n</code></pre>\n"
