    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>An answer that returns an Optional since the map may have no max value if it is empty:\n<code>map.entrySet().stream().max(Map.Entry.comparingByValue()).map(Map.Entry::getKey);</code></p>\n"
  }, {
