    "body" : "<p>Simple to understand.\nIn Below code, maxKey is the key which is holding the max value.</p>\n\n<pre><code>int maxKey = 0;\nint maxValue = 0;\nfor(int i : birds.keySet())\n{\n    if(birds.get(i) &gt; maxValue)\n    {\n        maxKey = i;\n        maxValue = birds.get(i);\n    }\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
