    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>This is going to return the keys with max value in a <code>Map&lt;Integer, Integer&gt;</code></p>\n<pre><code>public Set&lt;Integer&gt; getMaxKeys(Map&lt;Integer, Integer&gt; map) { \n\n        if (map.isEmpty()) {\n            return Collections.emptySet();\n        }\n\n        return map\n        .entrySet()\n        .stream()\n        .collect(\n            groupingBy(\n                Map.Entry::getValue, TreeMap::new, mapping(Map.Entry::getKey, toSet())\n            )\n         )\n         .lastEntry()\n         .getValue();\n    }\n</code></pre>\n"
